sub_title: Researcher | Consultant | Biotechnologist | Seeking New Opportunities in Biotechnology
summary:
Enthusiast undertaking research on algae to generate pharmaceutically-valuable products and an increased energy resource in the Institute of Molecular Biosciences, UQ. Profound experience working on the strategic development of automated high-throughput media optimization for a range of saltwater microalgae strains. Meritorious and highly motivated to publish my research. Experienced in the development of high-throughput screening systems for cyanobacteria and microalgae-based pigment production systems.
